Six Missouri residents, including two children, seemingly vanished after allegedly following the teachings of so-called “prophet” Rashad Jamal White in August. Neighbors witnessed the group appearing to worship to sun and run naked in their yard before their disappearance. Law&Crime’s Sierra Gillespie breaks down the disturbing disappearances.
